1.1
log
@The .Sm macro accepts at most one argument;
fixing an assertion failure found by jsg@@ with afl.
@
text
@.Dd November 26, 2014
.Dt SM-TWOARG 1
.Os OpenBSD
.Sh NAME
.Nm Sm-twoarg
.Nd spacing macro with multiple arguments
.Sh DESCRIPTION
.Sy default :
.Fl f Ar on
.br
.Sy off two :
.Sm off two
.Fl f Ar off
.br
.Sy bad two :
.Sm bad two
.Fl f Ar off
.br
.Sy on two :
.Sm on two
.Fl f Ar on
@
